        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.1",
          "pli": "“Sattimāni, bhikkhave, niddasavatthūni. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, there are these seven qualifications for graduation. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.2",
          "pli": "Katamāni satta? ",
          "en": "What seven? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.3",
          "pli": "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sikkhāsamādāne tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca sikkhāsamādāne avigatapemo, ",
          "en": "It’s when a mendicant has a keen enthusiasm to undertake the training … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.4",
          "pli": "dhammanisantiyā tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca dhammanisantiyā avigatapemo, ",
          "en": "to examine the teachings … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.5",
          "pli": "icchāvinaye tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca icchāvinaye avigatapemo, ",
          "en": "to get rid of desires … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.6",
          "pli": "paṭisallāne tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca paṭisallāne avigatapemo, ",
          "en": "for retreat … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.7",
          "pli": "vīriyārambhe tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca vīriyārambhe avigatapemo, ",
          "en": "to rouse up energy … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.8",
          "pli": "satinepakke tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca satinepakke avigatapemo, ",
          "en": "for mindfulness and alertness … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.9",
          "pli": "diṭṭhipaṭivedhe tibbacchando hoti āyatiñca diṭṭhipaṭivedhe avigatapemo. ",
          "en": "to penetrate theoretically. And they don’t lose these desires in the future. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.10",
          "pli": "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, satta niddasavatthūnī”ti. ",
          "en": "These are the seven qualifications for graduation.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.11",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:1.12",
          "pli": "Anusayavaggo dutiyo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:2.1",
          "pli": "Duve anusayā kulaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:2.2",
          "pli": "Puggalaṃ udakūpamaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:2.3",
          "pli": "Aniccaṃ dukkhaṃ anattā ca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an7.20:2.4",
          "pli": "Nibbānaṃ niddasavatthu cāti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
